            "content": [
              {
                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "Here’s the weather event history I found for **London, Ohio (Madison County area)** in the Weather table:\n\n- **Lake-Effect Snow** — **1/24/2007 9:00 AM**  \n  Lake-effect snow from the morning of the 24th into the afternoon of the 25th; heaviest snow the morning of the 25th (6–10\", locally higher).  \n  **Property damage:** $100,000 | **Crop:** $0 | **Injuries/Deaths:** 0/0  \n\n- **Winter Storm** — **2/13/2007 4:00 AM**  \n  Snow started early on the 13th, intensified during the afternoon; 8–13\" reported with gusty winds into the 14th.  \n  **Property damage:** $40,000 | **Crop:** $0 | **Injuries/Deaths:** 0/0  \n\n- **Winter Storm (separate report)** — **2/13/2007 4:00 AM**  \n  Snow and gusty winds from early on the 13th through the 14th; higher totals reported in surrounding areas.  \n  **Property damage:** $60,000 | **Crop:** $0 | **Injuries/Deaths:** 0/0  \n\n- **Flood** — **3/1/2007 11:30 PM**  \n  Several roads flooded/closed; some creeks out of banks across the county.  \n  **Property damage:** $3,000 | **Crop:** $0 | **Injuries/Deaths:** 0/0  \n\n- **Flood** — **3/14/2007 6:45 AM**  \n  Several roads flooded across the county.  \n  **Property damage:** $3,000 | **Crop:** $0 | **Injuries/Deaths:** 0/0  \n\n- **Winter Weather** — **12/7/2007 12:00 AM**  \n  About 2\" of snow measured at the county garage in London (lower amounts nearby).  \n  **Property damage:** $0 | **Crop:** $0 | **Injuries/Deaths:** 0/0  \n\nIf you tell me the **time range** you want (e.g., “all years available” vs. a specific decade), I can refine the results to just that period.",
